Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪和媽媽好像很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才怎麼好像聽到女孩的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是你幻聽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你聽 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 她到底有多大力氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼頂著櫃門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼呀 我只是靠在門上而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按世間常識來說 這個動作叫「頂著」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪 你該不會是把女生帶回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\3c&HBEC3B9&\c&H607350&\pos(537,85)\frx22\fry8\frz355.323}小雪在和媽媽說話。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\3c&HBEC3B9&\c&H607350&\frx22\fry8\frz357.172\pos(687,174)}小雪好像很開心。
